snippet.textDisplay: I am not saying that Alix looks bad at all, but I can understand why some people are saying she looks sick. Simply put, she used to wear makeup on Tasty videos. If someone wears makeup regularly, one of the few times you'll see them without makeup on is when they're sick. The makeup-free look becomes associated with illness. Therefore, Alix looks 'sick', because she looks like someone who isn't wearing makeup, which she isn't. Boom.
